{
  "name": "harness",
  "description": "Harness Engineering Agent：三条路径（fix/specify/brainstorm）+ 代码审查 + SDD（mispec）+ TDD + 结构化知识沉淀，AI Native 开发完整闭环。",
  "prompt": "file://~/.kiro/agents/harness.agent.md",
  "tools": ["*"],
  "allowedTools": ["*", "@*"],
  "toolsSettings": {
    "execute_bash": {
      "autoAllowReadonly": true,
      "allowedCommands": [".*"],
      "deniedCommands": [
        "rm -rf /.*",
        "rm -rf ~.*",
        "rm .*",
        "rmdir .*",
        "mkfs\\..*",
        "dd if=.*of=/dev/.*",
        ":\\(\\)\\{ :\\|:& \\};:.*",
        "chmod -R 777 /.*",
        "chown -R .* /.*",
        "git push .* --force.*",
        "git clean -fdx.*",
        "repo forall .* -c .* git clean.*",
        "repo forall .* -c .* git reset --hard.*"
      ]
    }
  },
  "mcpServers": {
    "executor": {
      "command": "executor-mcp"
    },
    "feishu-mcp": {
      "url": "<YOUR_FEISHU_MCP_URL>"
    }
  },
  "resources": [
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/session-handoff/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/vela-harness/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/vela-build/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/vela-run/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/vela-review/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/harness-lessons/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/unit-test-gen/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/test-driven-development/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/cmocka-unit-test/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/gtest-unit-test/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/executor/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/git-commit/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/git-worktree/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/repoworktree/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/spec-design/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/mispec.change-propagation/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/experience-summarize/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/ce-brainstorm/SKILL.md",
    "skill://~/.kiro/skills/interactive-form/SKILL.md",
    "file://~/.kiro/steering/**/*.md",
    "file://.harness/lessons-learned.md",
    "file://.harness/PROGRESS.md"
  ],
  "welcomeMessage": "🔧 Harness Engineering Agent 就绪。\n\n三条路径：\n  fix <描述>       — 快速修复（小改动，目标清晰）\n  specify <描述>   — 完整开发（大改动，目标清晰）\n  brainstorm <描述> — 探索设计（大改动，目标模糊）\n\n其他命令：\n  init          — 初始化项目 .harness/ 目录\n  plan          — 技术方案\n  tasks         — 任务拆解\n  implement     — TDD 实现\n  review        — 代码审查（commit 前）\n  verify        — 编译+测试+门禁\n  todo          — 查看待办\n  search <词>   — 搜索经验\n  evolve        — 收尾+知识沉淀\n  status        — 查看进度\n  loop          — 全自动闭环\n\n输入 init 开始，或直接描述需求。"
}
